      • getActionsRating

        public static ActionsRating getActionsRating​(IPlayer self,
                                             Board<Cell> board)
        Calculates the ActionsRating for the given IPlayer on the given Board. The ActionsRating is favoring actions slower speeds.
        Parameters:

      • ratingValue

        private static double ratingValue​(IPlayer parent,
                                  IPlayer child)
        Calculates the single rating value for two players. One has to be the parent, one the child.
        Calculation: 0 (speed up), 0.5 (keeping speed), 1 (slow down)
        Parameters:
        parent - IPlayer parent
        child - IPlayer child
        Returns:
        rating value result as double
